overview: Summer in the city is always a magical time, especially in a place as wonderful as Amsterdam; but it's made even more magical when you're confronted with the kind of blissful sex-addicts that make up the cast in this terrific offering from Amsterdam Amateurs. Truth is, they make those glorious months in the middle of the year seem even hotter than is otherwise the case. What's more, they're clearly more than happy to get up to their antics in the great outdoors; making the most of every opportunity to act like animals in the woods. No question about it, you're gonna love these filthy fuckers as they rut to their hearts' content; serving up a delicious performance of raunchy wild action, with lashings of pent up spunk!
title: Summer Makes Me Wet
